data.description: NEW PRICE !!!!!!This beautiful home is located just outside of Arlington city limit. Only 30 min from Blue Oval  on 4 acres with a mixture of trees and open spaces located in a quiet neighborhood. It has plenty of entertainment space and lots of room for children to play. This 5 br. 3.1ba has 3500 sq ft with hardwood floors & tile downstairs and new carpet upstairs. Lots of natural light and a large patio over looking the pool area. Call and make an appointment to see this beautiful property.
